[SN]TITLE[SN]
Woman killed in Boxing Day house fire in Stoke-on-Trent named

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 60-year-old woman who died in a house fire in Stoke-on-Trent on Boxing Day has been named by police.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Karen Bowden was pronounced dead at the scene the fire at Bayham Walk in Bucknall.
A man in his 60s who was taken to hospital after being recovered from the house has been discharged.
Staffordshire Police said it was not treating the fire as suspicious. A report is being prepared for the coroner.
